,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"뭐냐니 말할 것도 없지.\n즐거운 일이야!\n이 내가 즐거운 걸 찾지 않으면 뭘 하겠어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-001-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"하나사키가와 학생1","body":"뭘 하냐니, 어어……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"하나사키가와 학생2","body":"아. 괜찮아, 츠루마키는 맨날 저러니까.\n「즐거운 일 찾기」가 일과야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"이런~ 생각나지 않나 보네.\n그렇지만 괜찮아! 다른 사람한테도 물어볼게!\n아무튼, 고마워!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-001-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"……엇, 그렇지!\n좋~~은 게 생각났어!\n돌격, 돌격~!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-001-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"하나사키가와 학생1","body":"가 버렸다…… 뭔가…… 엄청난 사람이네……\n왜 즐거운 일을 찾는 거지……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"하나사키가와 학생2","body":"글쎄……\n우리 학교에서 저 사람의\n머릿속을 알만한 학생은 없을 것 같아……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"라~~♪ 랄랄라~~♪ 랄랄라라~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"band3-001-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"통행인1","body":"!? 뭐야, 저 여고생.\n갑자기 아카펠라로 노래하기 시작했는데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"코코로","body":"라~♪ ……으~~음? 아직도 즐겁지 않네.\n뭔가 부족한 걸까?\n이대로는 온 세상을 웃는 얼굴로 만들 수 없어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"moti